4.11.18 hud-color-frame-fg
--------------------------

 -- Command-line option: `--hud-color-frame-fg=<value>'
 -- Environment variable: `LW6_HUD_COLOR_FRAME_FG'
 -- XML key: `hud-color-frame-fg'
     Type: color

     Default value: #ccc

